1012

 

Field identifier (Name):

1012 (ALPHANUMERIC IDENTIFIER)

 

 

Definition:

AN IDENTIFIER OR INDEX TO REFER TO AN INSTANCE OF AN ENTITY, COMMONLY CONSIDERED AS AN 'INDEX' OR 'NUMBER', BUT NOT NECESSARILY A NUMERIC.

 

 

Sponsor:

None

 

 

Remarks:

None

 

 

Related Documents:         

NONE

 

 

Status:  

In Service

 

 

Field Version:

1.0
